metadata.description: ¡Prepárate, el invierno está llegando!  Spanish humorist José Fonollosa brings us a rollicking parody in the finest Mad Magazine tradition.  The Storks, Moneysters, Burgerkings and more squabble over the stupidest things while the Tortugyens prepare to unleash their ultimate weapon: Danone Tortugyen's phenomenal bustline!
metadata.name: Shame of Thrones
